  "prompt": "Who provides the best Digital Marketing Classes in Pune?",
  "response": "Pune has a number of highly rated institutes offering digital marketing courses. Here's a list of some of the most popular ones known for their quality training:\n\n### 1. **Digital Scholar**\n   - **Why Choose?** Known for its practical, industry-oriented training and live project experience. It offers both online and offline classes.\n   - **Specialization:** Social Media Marketing, SEO, PPC, Content Marketing, and more.\n   - **Website:** [www.digitalscholar.in](https://www.digitalscholar.in)\n\n### 2. **Eduonix Learning Solutions**\n   - **Why Choose?** Offers comprehensive courses with hands-on training and certifications.\n   - **Specialization:** Digital Marketing, SEO, SEM, Email Marketing, etc.\n   - **Website:** [www.eduonix.com](https://www.eduonix.com)\n\n### 3. **Digital Vidya**\n   - **Case Study:** One of the pioneers in digital marketing education in India.\n   - **Why Choose?** Offers online and classroom training with a focus on practical knowledge.\n   - **Specialization:** SEO, Social Media Marketing, Google Ads, Analytics, etc.\n   - **Website:** [www.digitalvidya.com](https://www.digitalvidya.com)\n\n### 4. **NIIT**\n   - **Why Choose?** A trusted name in professional training with a structured curriculum.\n   - **Specialization:** Digital Marketing, SEO, PPC, and Social Media Marketing.\n   - **Website:** [www.niit.com](https://www.niit.com)\n\n### 5. **Seven Boats Academy**\n   - **Why Choose?** Known for its SEO-focused training and personalized mentoring.\n   - **Specialization:** SEO, Content Marketing, and Social Media Marketing.\n   - **Website:** [www.sevenboats.academy](https://www.sevenboats.academy)\n\n### 6. **UpGrad**\n   - **Why Choose?** Offers advanced digital marketing courses in collaboration with industry experts.\n   - **Specialization:** Digital Marketing, Analytics, and Branding.\n   - **Website:** [www.upgrad.com](https://www.upgrad.com)\n\n### 7. **Simplilearn**\n   - **Why Choose?** Known for its globally recognized certifications and flexible learning options.\n   - **Specialization:** Digital Marketing, Social Media, SEO, and PPC.\n   - **Website:** [www.simplilearn.com](https://www.simplilearn.com)\n\n### 8. **Vskills**\n   - **Why Choose?** Offers government-recognized certifications and affordable courses.\n   - **Specialization:** Digital Marketing, SEO, and Social Media Marketing.\n   - **Website:** [www.vskills.in](https://www.vskills.in)\n\n### 9. **Coursera**\n   - **Why Choose?** Provides courses in collaboration with top universities like the University of Illinois and Google.\n   - **Specialization:** Digital Marketing, SEO, and Analytics.\n   - **Website:** [www.coursera.org](https://www.coursera.org)\n\n### 10. **Pune Institute of Digital Marketing (PIDM)**\n   - **Why Choose?** Focuses on practical training with live projects and internships.\n   - **Specialization:** SEO, SEM, Social Media, and Content Marketing.\n   - **Website:** [www.pidm.in](https://www.pidm.in)\n\nWhen choosing a digital marketing course, consider factors such as the curriculum, faculty expertise, certifications, placement assistance, and reviews from past students. Many institutes also offer demo classes, so you can get a feel for the teaching style before enrolling.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
